Reasoning: 
1. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning method for designing an end-to-end vision-based ACC system. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The proposed ACC system is vision-based and uses feature data for training and testing. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics): The ACC system is designed for vehicles and involves controlling their speed and distance from other vehicles on a highway. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses reinforcement learning to train the ACC system. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper involves designing a control system for vehicles on a highway.
